===Etymology===
From a variant of the {{etyl|enm|en}} noun {{term|even|lang=enm}} (itself from {{etyl|ang|en}} {{term|æfen|ǣfen|lang=ang}}, with a pre-1200 loss of the terminal '-n', which was mistaken for an inflection. <ref>http://dictionary.reference.com/browse/eve</ref> See also the now archaic or poetic {{term|even||evening|lang=en}}, from the same source.

